OL,3,CUrgent 999 appeal in desperate search
OL,4,Cfor missing 10-year-old girl
OL,6,FDetectives have shared an urgent
OL,7,Fappeal for help to trace a missing 10-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl last seen riding a pink
OL,9,Fbike.
OL,11,FRosie May Osborne is missing from
OL,12,FBootle in Merseyside.
OL,14,FThe youngster was last seen in North
OL,15,FPark on Stanley Road in Bootle at
OL,16,Faround 8am on Sunday 19 July.
OL,18,FShe is described as 5ft tall, slim
OL,19,Fbuild, with blonde wavy hair and wears
OL,20,Fglasses. When last seen, she was
OL,21,Friding a pink bike.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
