OL,3,CUrgent 999 appeal in desperate search
OL,4,Cfor missing 10-year-old girl
OL,6,FShe often visits parks in the Bootle
OL,7,Farea.
OL,9,FA spokesperson for Merseyside Police
OL,10,Fsaid enquiries have been ongoing
OL,11,Fovernight to find her.
OL,13,FIf you see Rosie, please call 999 as
OL,14,Fsoon as possible so police can make
OL,15,Fsure she is safe.
